text: Jean-Gilles Hnamuko (born 2 March 1996) is a New Caledonian international footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Luxembourgish club Jeunesse Junglinster. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:New Caledonian footballers Category:People from Nouméa Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:AS Mont-Dore players Category:AS Lössi players Category:Racing Club de France Football players Category:US Roye-Noyon players Category:R.D.
